  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to gain a better understanding of the effects of exercise and
      cognitive training on improving brain function in healthy older adults who may be at risk for
      developing Alzheimer's Disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
